                        <tr>
                           <td>The patient shows marked dyslipidemia with significantly elevated total cholesterol and LDL, and low HDL levels. This lipid profile is associated with increased cardiovascular risk. Clinical correlation and consideration of lifestyle modification and/or lipid-lowering therapy are recommended. Regular monitoring is advised.</td>
